   [0.1E74?OpenElement&FieldElemFormat=jpg] NOTICE: Effective
   approximately March 1, 2002, the RACER system will no longer be
   available.
   This change is necessary because of the migration from our old Bancap
   database to the new Case Management/Electronic Case Filing system
   (CM/ECF). Public access to this new system is available through Pacer
   (A Pacer account is required, as there will be a charge of 7 cents per
   page to view documents). To learn more about Pacer and how to register,
   click here.
   Information found on our Racer website is currently being transferred
   to Pacer. Until the migration is complete:
   * Visit our Pacer website for documents filed from January 1, 2002 to
   the present.
   * Visit the Racer website for documents filed from 1998 to December 27,
   2001.
   Case Dockets Online - View Case Docket Information and images using our
   RACER system for cases filed from 1998 through December 27, 2001.
   To view documents in the Washington Group International, Inc. case,
   please click on the RACER link above. In the space for "case number",
   type 01-31627 or go to Pacer.
   For administrative or procedural information in Washington Group
   International, Inc., click here for links to specific documents.
   To view documents in the AgriBioTech case, please click on the RACER
   link above. In the space for "case number", type 00-10533 or go to
   Pacer.
   For administrative or procedural information in AgriBioTech Inc.,
   AgriBioTech Canada, Inc., Las Vegas Fertilizer, Co., Garden West
   Distributors, Inc., or George W. Hill & Co. click here for links to
   specific documents.
   To view documents in the National Airlines case, please click on the
   RACER link above. In the space for "case number", type 00-19258 or go
   to Pacer.
   For administrative or procedural information in National Airlines,
   click here for links to specific documents.
   ______________________________________________________
   Hearing Calendars Online - View daily hearing calendars for Nevada
   Bankruptcy Judges as well as AgriBioTech.
   Calendars are updated on a daily basis. Consequently, the calendars may
   be modified several times prior to the actual hearing date.
   To view calendars for Judges Gregg W. Zive, Linda B. Riegle, Robert C.
   Jones, and Bert M. Goldwater, click here.
   To view calendars for Washington Group International, click here.
   To view calendars for AgriBioTech, click here.
   To view calendars for National Airlines, click here.
   ______________________________________________________
   The regular business hours of the Office of the Clerk are 9:00a.m. to
   4:00p.m. all days except Saturdays, Sundays and legal holidays.
   This web site contains hypertext links or pointers to external web
   sites. These links or pointers are provided for the user's convenience.
   The Bankruptcy Court does not control or guarantee the accuracy,
   relevance, timeliness or completeness of this outside information.
   Further, the inclusion of links or pointers to particular items in
   hypertext is not intended to reflect their importance, nor is it
   intended to endorse any views expressed, or products or services
   offered, on these outside sites, or the organizations sponsoring the
   sites.
   MISSION STATEMENT:
   The mission of the United States Bankruptcy Court for the District of
   Nevada is to resolve matters fairly and timely within the jurisdiction
   of the court in accordance with the Constitution and laws of the United
   States by providing an impartial, independent, and dignified forum, in
   order to promote respect for the rule of law, engender public
   confidence and trust, and protect individual rights and liberties.
   Feel free to go to our Guestbook area, and fill out a survey or leave
   your comments. The Links page offers other relevant court web sites.

